%N A395668 Expansion of g^5*(3-2*g)/(5-4*g)^2, where g = 1+x*g^5 is the g.f. of A002294.
%F A395668 Sum_{k>=1} a(k-1) * x^k/k = (1/10) * log( Sum_{k>=0} binomial(5*k+5,k) * x^k ).
%F A395668 a(n) = A395665(n)/(n+1) = (1/10) * (binomial(5*n+4,n) + Sum_{k=0..n+1} 4^(n+1-k) * binomial(5*n+5,k)).
%o A395668 (PARI) a(n) = (binomial(5*n+4, n)+sum(k=0, n+1, 4^(n+1-k)*binomial(5*n+5, k)))/10;
